column16: Darwin Barney pops out to first baseman Todd Helton in foul territory.

Ryan Dempster out on a sacrifice bunt to first baseman Todd Helton.    Geovany Soto to 2nd.
Kosuke Fukudome grounds out, second baseman Jonathan Herrera to first baseman Todd Helton.

Aramis Ramirez singles on a ground ball to left fielder Carlos Gonzalez.    Starlin Castro scores.    Darwin Barney to 2nd.
Darwin Barney singles on a ground ball to center fielder Dexter Fowler.    Starlin Castro to 2nd.
Ryan Dempster flies out to center fielder Dexter Fowler.

Aramis Ramirez grounds out, pitcher Alan Johnson to first baseman Todd Helton.
